"{\"uid\": \"today.com-news-paris-olympics-andy-macdonald-skateboarder-paris-olympics-2024-rcna165588\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"A Michael Kors Bag, Suede Slippers and More Holiday Gifts at Walmart - Starting at $9    Gina Vivinetto  Andy Macdonald may have spent decades as a professional skateboarder, but the veteran athlete was an excited newcomer at the 2024 Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 250, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 14, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Kors\", \"score\": 0.9999754394710898, \"rank\": 2.4561132171954717e-05, \"text\": \"Michael Kors\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Kors\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Kors\"}, {\"begin\": 105, \"end\": 119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Macdonald_(skateboarder)\", \"score\": 0.9999978194979248, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andy Macdonald\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Macdonald_(skateboarder)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Macdonald_(skateboarder)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Aug. 7, the 51-year-old Macdonald was cheered on by fellow skateboarding legend Tony Hawk, 56, as he became the oldest skateboarder to ever compete in an Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 252, \"to\": 423, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Macdonald went pro in 1994 and is decades older than his fellowTeam Great Britain skateboarders, 16-year-olds Sky Brown and Lola Tambling.\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 562, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 492, \"end\": 505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9998007002947429, \"rank\": 0.00019544647199297086, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 534, \"end\": 543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Brown\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sky Brown\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Brown\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Brown\"}, {\"begin\": 548, \"end\": 552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lola_Cars\", \"score\": 0.999995970338593, \"rank\": 4.02914617194674e-06, \"text\": \"Lola\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lola_Cars\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lola_Cars\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Macdonald, a 23-time X Games champion, zipped through the skatepark during the preliminaries Wednesday, showing off flashy moves including a madonna and a body varial 540.\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 735, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While he did not win a medal, Macdonald is calling the experience the thrill of his professional career.\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 841, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I could have fallen on every run and just be as happy as I am now.\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 910, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It does not matter,\\\" MacdonaldtoldOlympics.comafter the event.\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 973, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's just been the experience of a lifetime.\\\"\", \"from\": 974, \"to\": 1020, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After Macdonald arrived in Paris, he spent several days exploring and getting to know his fellow athletes, he said.\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1137, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1049, \"end\": 1054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999989736352, \"rank\": 1.0264373868546304e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was getting like, four hours of sleep because I was up in the Olympic Village.\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1220, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1204, \"end\": 1219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.4773610510668133e-12, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I bought an electric skateboard so I was just zooming around, just like meeting everybody,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1321, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a really beautiful thing to be a part of; just being here, being an Olympian,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 1417, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1397, \"end\": 1405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999932124142816, \"rank\": 6.78763172108498e-06, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And then today was even more special.\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1456, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Like the icing on the cake that I got to be here and participate.\\\"\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1523, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Skateboarding is arelatively new sport at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1580, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It debuted in 2021 at the Tokyo Summer Games and has already been approved for the Los Angeles Games in 2028,per NBC Olympics.\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1707, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1664, \"end\": 1675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999899525847, \"rank\": 9.940997401161125e-09, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 1694, \"end\": 1706, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBC Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Macdonald first hinted at his plans to compete in an Olympics in an August 2022 poston Instagram.\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1806, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1796, \"end\": 1805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3053123563494618e-21, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athlete, who was born and raised just outside Boston, Massachusetts, and holds dual citizenship because of his English-born father, revealed at the time that he qualified forGreat Britain's national skateboard park team.\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 2032, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1866, \"end\": 1879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Massachusetts\", \"score\": 0.9999938122085037, \"rank\": 2.2776982808860997e-06, \"text\": \"Massachusetts\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Massachusetts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Massachusetts\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hawk, who clapped for his former vert doubles partner at Wednesday's event, told Olympic organizers he was \\\"proud\\\" of Macdonald - but hardly surprised by his tenacity.\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2201, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Andy is a prime example of how much discipline can pay off,\\\" he said, adding, \\\"You can always count on him to do something amazing.\\\"\", \"from\": 2203, \"to\": 2336, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Peacock\\u00a0is streaming the Paris Olympics around the clock.Learn more about accounts here.\", \"from\": 2338, \"to\": 2426, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TODAY\\u00a0earns a commission\\u00a0on\\u00a0purchases.\", \"from\": 2427, \"to\": 2465, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Peacock\\u00a0is owned by our parent company NBCUniversal.\", \"from\": 2466, \"to\": 2518, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2505, \"end\": 2517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.999998799916322, \"rank\": 1.1505168956575312e-06, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gina Vivinetto is a trending news reporter for TODAY.com  \\u00a9\\u00a02025 NBCUniversal Media, LLCApple\\u00ae, Apple logo\\u00ae and App Store\\u00ae are registered trademarks of Apple Inc.\", \"from\": 2520, \"to\": 2682, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2520, \"end\": 2524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gina_Austin\", \"score\": 0.7989810404863822, \"rank\": 0.2515941547137882, \"text\": \"Gina\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gina_Austin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gina_Austin\"}, {\"begin\": 2567, \"end\": 2576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Today_(American_TV_program)\", \"score\": 0.999839595647005, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"TODAY.com\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Today_(American_TV_program)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Today_(American_TV_program)\"}, {\"begin\": 2616, \"end\": 2621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Inc.\", \"score\": 0.9999999692881834, \"rank\": 3.070572667187046e-08, \"text\": \"Apple\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Inc.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Apple_Inc.\"}, {\"begin\": 2632, \"end\": 2641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mac_App_Store\", \"score\": 0.7284816445218236,